Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.85,0:00:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,掌上的微風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.75,0:00:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在光芒中一閃一閃地舞動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.36,0:00:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經能用全新的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.40,0:00:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向陌生人道早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.11,0:00:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,儘管回憶溢滿心頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.05,0:00:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的朝氣絕不認輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.62,0:00:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無所謂在乾掉的淚痕中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.09,0:00:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一扇通往夢想的門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.16,0:01:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果煩惱就無法前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.27,0:01:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.70,0:01:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會以迎接朋友的方式\N溫柔地微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.17,0:01:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.81,0:01:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無意間悲傷雖然湧上心頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.28,0:01:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也會試著與人和好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.69,0:01:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.50,0:01:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(自助洗衣店)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.20,0:01:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒辦法,帶回公寓曬吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.67,0:01:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天氣也蠻不錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.58,0:02:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天氣雖然不錯\N不過那個陽台很恐怖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.66,0:02:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怪叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.52,0:02:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個怪叔叔到底想幹嘛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.33,0:02:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#22 五代深受打擊!響子的辭職宣言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.74,0:03:00.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慢慢地倒熱水進去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.10,0:03:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀,好像倒太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.37,0:03:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.21,0:03:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來…來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.25,0:03:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.65,0:03:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?有詭異的男人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.28,0:03:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊,戴著一副墨鏡\N感覺很凶狠的中年男子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.46,0:03:18.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.56,0:03:22.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管…管理員!太危險了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.93,0:03:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,萬一是個變態,妳要怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.60,0:03:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會有事的啦,我只是看看而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.18,0:03:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連個人影都沒有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.65,0:03:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪,這就怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.25,0:03:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂,那個躲在電線桿後面的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.52,0:03:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.66,0:03:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂,給我站住!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.49,0:03:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯吧,管理員\N那個人很可疑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.66,0:04:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能是闖空門的或是縱火犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.70,0:04:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看起來像這種人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.10,0:04:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會是偷內褲的賊嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.77,0:04:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看他那付德行,一定錯不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.77,0:04:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣子嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.81,0:04:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為他真的長得一付\N色狼變態的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.74,0:04:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這…這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.01,0:04:19.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次再來的話\N還是打110報警比較好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.85,0:04:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個…\N什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.89,0:04:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.56,0:04:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.40,0:04:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳爸爸?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.67,0:04:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳是在騙我的吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.54,0:04:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個背影,錯不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.74,0:04:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思,驚擾你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.55,0:04:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.88,0:04:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.08,0:04:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難怪我覺得他是個有氣質\N且文質彬彬的紳士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.12,0:04:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很有中年男子的魅力…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.35,0:04:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被誤會也是沒辦法的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.42,0:05:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰叫他那樣鬼鬼祟祟的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.26,0:05:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來背後好像有複雜的隱情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.51,0:05:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小津江,妳有沒有\N跟妳爸爸吵過架?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.11,0:05:22.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼突然問我這種問題?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.88,0:05:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有什麼特別的意思啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.78,0:05:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是想知道父女關係\N是怎麼一回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.96,0:05:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我爸爸好像不知道\N要怎麼跟我相處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.80,0:05:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能是很害羞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.97,0:05:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比如說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.23,0:05:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是打個比方喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.57,0:05:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女兒不顧反對硬要結婚的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.74,0:05:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳爸爸會有什麼反應呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.48,0:05:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我爸爸沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.45,0:05:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他跟你一定合得來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.62,0:06:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我爸跟我說,交了男朋友\N一定要帶回家給他看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.12,0:06:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他要觀察這個男生\N看看是不是真能把女兒交給他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.49,0:06:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果這樣他還不滿意呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.46,0:06:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.50,0:06:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他可能會說\N兩個人都還太年輕吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.90,0:06:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是在講誰跟誰啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.42,0:06:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打個電話看看好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.50,0:06:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.90,0:06:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正他要說什麼\N我都知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.60,0:06:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定是叫我回家\N然後叫我再婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.57,0:06:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,錯不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.61,0:07:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂,這裡是一刻館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.81,0:07:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊,媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.55,0:07:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳沒有見到爸爸是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.15,0:07:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大致的情況我都聽說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.62,0:07:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼!他逃走了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.13,0:07:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,害我丟臉丟死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.56,0:07:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,房客還以為他是個變態色狼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.60,0:07:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,變態色狼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.77,0:07:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂,老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.17,0:07:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說響子不在是騙我的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.44,0:07:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊?什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.54,0:07:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們到底想怎樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.81,0:07:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,電話裡說不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.08,0:07:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下星期天回家來一趟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.91,0:07:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.38,0:07:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正妳過年也沒回來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.72,0:07:43.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽到了吧,等妳回來喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.23,0:07:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把理由說清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.80,0:07:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你為什麼逃掉了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.86,0:07:55.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼關係\N反正我已經看到公寓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.63,0:08:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公,就是因為你這種態度\N響子才不肯回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.14,0:08:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼說?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.27,0:08:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她是在我們極力反對之下結婚的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.58,0:08:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣她怎麼會放棄呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.71,0:08:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我這麼做也是為了響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.88,0:08:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以下星期天…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.25,0:08:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的,妳看惣一郎\N不是很快就死了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.05,0:08:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當初她就應該選個\N年輕力壯的才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.56,0:08:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都過去的事了\N你要唸到什麼時候啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.33,0:08:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你再唸的話\N我就跟你離婚喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.50,0:08:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,律子,妳怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.71,0:08:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真討厭\N我該用什麼表情進去呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.11,0:08:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看爸爸上次的樣子\N好像還很生氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.39,0:08:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是擺出笑容比較好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.06,0:08:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯,裝作沒事的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.30,0:09:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後笑一笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.87,0:09:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.74,0:09:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗨…響子,妳回來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.34,0:09:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼!這是什麼意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.75,0:09:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要我辭掉管理員的工作嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.62,0:09:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊,就是這個意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.22,0:09:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,況且,那種破爛公寓\N不是年輕女孩子該待的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.09,0:09:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這麼說太過份了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.06,0:09:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再怎麼破爛\N那也是我工作的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.36,0:09:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子,問題不在公寓的外觀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.47,0:09:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那棟一刻館的房東\N是惣一郎他們家的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.37,0:09:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算是工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.24,0:09:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老是跟過世老公的婆家\N牽扯不清…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.04,0:09:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不太妥當吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.94,0:09:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼好不妥當的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.85,0:09:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,更糟糕的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.88,0:09:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖說是房客,但跟那麼年輕的男人\N共住在一個屋簷下,實在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.29,0:09:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,年輕的男人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.82,0:09:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你指的是五代嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.72,0:10:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不管他叫什麼名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.62,0:10:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不能讓再婚之前的\N寶貝女兒受到任何傷害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.70,0:10:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼歪理啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.13,0:10:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給我搬回來住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.63,0:10:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.37,0:10:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我把話說在前頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.87,0:10:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是為了音無家的義理人情\N才在那裡當管理員的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.41,0:10:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是因為喜歡那個地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.01,0:10:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以絕不辭職
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.45,0:10:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子,妳偶爾也乖乖地\N聽從父母的話是會怎麼樣!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.72,0:10:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不高興的話\N要不要斷絕父女關係?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.16,0:10:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子,不要這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.79,0:10:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一點都不可愛,這到底像誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.90,0:10:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之,我要妳辭掉一刻館的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.97,0:10:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不辭!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.33,0:10:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.00,0:10:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子,妳這是什麼坐姿啊\N太沒教養了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.60,0:10:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不辭就是不辭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.81,0:10:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我聽不到就是聽不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.78,0:10:52.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不辭職
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.68,0:10:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我聽不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.61,0:10:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不…不要吵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.05,0:10:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.88,0:10:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣啦!爸爸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.76,0:11:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,破爛公寓是嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.97,0:11:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那又怎樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.50,0:11:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡是我的家啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.37,0:11:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對,沒錯,這裡是我的家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.55,0:12:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天也要好好加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.38,0:12:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀,妳在整修地板啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.58,0:12:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊,做一點緊急處置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.25,0:12:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也來幫忙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.99,0:12:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.86,0:12:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想要自己來做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.63,0:12:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本沒有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.13,0:12:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,樑柱早就蛀爛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.63,0:12:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.23,0:12:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概還可以撐上一陣子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.04,0:13:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那裡不行!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.64,0:13:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.55,0:13:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次我會叫木工來修
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.39,0:13:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯,那樣比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.03,0:13:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,破爛的公寓也無所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.03,0:13:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且房客,換個方向想想\N也都是一些好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.80,0:13:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼!\N她跟五代在陽台上抱在一起?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.84,0:13:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊,一大早就抱在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.11,0:13:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們真的很相愛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.58,0:13:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.95,0:13:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而…而且房租都有按時繳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.98,0:13:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員\N什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.45,0:13:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個月的房租\N能不能讓我延一下?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.16,0:13:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.60,0:14:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓…讓你延吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.16,0:14:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過不能拖太久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.60,0:14:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.47,0:14:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼?\N好像篤定我會答應似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.91,0:14:13.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕不能認輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.28,0:14:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊,這種事我應該已經習慣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.98,0:14:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.38,0:14:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們大家在看什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.52,0:14:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要一刻館還在\N我絕不辭掉管理員的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.12,0:14:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是白蟻耶!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.99,0:14:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.43,0:14:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡大概快垮了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.70,0:15:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問,這些藥\N會噴在建築物裡面嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.53,0:15:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用,只要再灌點藥\N然後,塗上點藥就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.30,0:15:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.68,0:15:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吵死了,一大清早的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.28,0:15:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,木工來了,正在做工啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.02,0:15:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們兩個怎麼這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.79,0:15:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太沒規矩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.72,0:15:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於要修理陽台了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.42,0:15:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,外面還在驅除白蟻呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.99,0:15:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來這次很認真喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.70,0:15:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果其它還有想修理的地方\N管理員要我們儘管跟她說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.77,0:15:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,我想把牆洞給補起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.47,0:15:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去拜託她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.01,0:15:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.31,0:15:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請讓開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.38,0:15:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.98,0:16:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你實在太無情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.42,0:16:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.75,0:16:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個牆洞\N是我跟你聯絡感情的地方啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.66,0:16:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老實跟你說\N我不想跟你聯絡感情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.13,0:16:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別理他們,請繼續修理吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.70,0:16:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是過份,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.80,0:16:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是心靈相通的好朋友啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.54,0:16:25.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰跟你心靈相通啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.94,0:16:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好不容易才挖通的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.38,0:16:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是侵犯到我的隱私權
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.85,0:16:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真的非補不可?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.65,0:16:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯,非補不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.79,0:16:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在深夜,我聽到五代的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.03,0:16:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀,他在說什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.06,0:16:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,於是我豎耳傾聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.40,0:16:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.97,0:16:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的確聽到他這麼叫著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.41,0:17:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呼吸很急促
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.15,0:17:02.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.45,0:17:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,於是我從牆洞偷看了一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.72,0:17:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.32,0:17:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太暗了,什麼都看不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.26,0:17:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,深夜,他一邊呼喚管理員的名字\N一邊在做什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.56,0:17:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是令人猜不透啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.46,0:17:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在我的房間做什麼事\N是我的自由吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.07,0:17:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好灰暗喔,好灰暗的青春啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.20,0:17:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太淒慘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.57,0:17:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要去跟管理員說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.61,0:17:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.58,0:17:35.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到你居然看開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.48,0:17:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可不會老是受你威脅的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.25,0:17:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們在幹嘛\N這可不是話劇表演喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.05,0:17:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但比話劇還好看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.89,0:17:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你似乎太小看我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.50,0:17:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代把管理員…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.07,0:18:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當作發洩性慾的工具!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.17,0:18:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正外面又聽不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.48,0:18:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過樓梯這裡聽得到哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.19,0:18:19.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼啦?五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.26,0:18:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代\N是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.03,0:18:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會去請水泥匠來補\N請你先把房間收拾一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.00,0:18:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.33,0:18:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很早就想修補5號房的牆壁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.64,0:18:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要轉移話題\N我們現在應該談的是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.97,0:18:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,牆壁修補好了\N你就不會聽到怪聲了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.54,0:18:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒立場說話了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.25,0:18:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.55,0:18:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於告了一個段落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.59,0:18:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有什麼地方需要修的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.50,0:19:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這棟公寓看來還不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.34,0:19:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白蟻也沒有造成什麼大問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.68,0:19:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂,一刻…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.85,0:19:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞什麼,是媽媽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.82,0:19:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼口氣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.39,0:19:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳這是什麼口氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.33,0:19:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經跟妳爸商量過了\N關於辭去管理員工作的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.33,0:19:36.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等,我不是說過不辭職嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.93,0:19:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想直接找房東談一談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.30,0:19:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要這樣啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.08,0:19:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我這麼做是為了妳好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.68,0:19:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳要是敢跟音無家亂說的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.65,0:19:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真的會跟你們斷絕親子關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.26,0:19:59.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請妳好好記住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.96,0:20:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們把女兒當成什麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.26,0:20:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要小看我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.77,0:20:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要小看妳的父母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.02,0:20:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要回家嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.22,0:20:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊,大嬸妳出來買東西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.86,0:20:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊,晚飯的菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.66,0:20:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不覺得\N最近管理員怪怪的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.80,0:20:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然開始大肆整修起公寓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.33,0:20:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是一件好事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.63,0:20:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過太突然了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.94,0:20:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說來,好像真的有點…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.94,0:20:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯吧,你也是這麼覺得的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.25,0:20:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這背後一定有什麼問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.48,0:20:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼問題?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.44,0:21:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗨,我們回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.07,0:21:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼啦?惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.58,0:21:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀,還沒吃晚飯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.45,0:21:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.79,0:21:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.95,0:21:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員居然忘記餵惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.39,0:21:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她跑到哪裡去了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.86,0:21:46.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能又是去找工人\N來修理什麼了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.83,0:22:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人在嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.46,0:22:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您是哪位?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.63,0:22:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個…我是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.94,0:22:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,音無響子的母親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.94,0:22:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天我是來拜訪各位房客的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.51,0:22:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜訪房客?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.45,0:22:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底有什麼事啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.95,0:22:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.62,0:22:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.99,0:22:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感謝各位長久以來\N這麼照顧我們響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.18,0:23:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,音無響子從今天開始\N辭去一刻館的管理員工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.70,0:23:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辭…辭職?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.42,0:23:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝大家的關心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.49,0:23:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不打算辭職
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.53,0:23:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.03,0:24:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.90,0:24:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「響子千鈞一!\N母親可怕的陰謀!」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.43,0:24:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我永遠都是一刻館的管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:28.19,0:24:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那天在陌生的城市下了一場陣雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:36.10,0:24:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳非常在意淋溼的高跟鞋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:43.07,0:24:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從前妳用那隱藏著\N稚氣的側臉和我交談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:51.08,0:24:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳說的話語至今仍能想起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:57.29,0:25:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一開始就彷佛\N置身電影中的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:05.03,0:25:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳輕聲細語地說著\N安靜的最後一幕

